    <Descriptive_Notes>
      <Descriptive_Note>
        <Note_Text>In Buddhism, objects or images considered "auspicious images," for example, an image of the Buddha that had a miraculous appearance or characteristics considered to be a sign of divine favor.</Note_Text>
